liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: It was coming for a long time. The cross came in and landed at the feet of Ana-Maria Crnogorcevic. The shot was saved by Olivia McDaniel, another shot was fired, again saved by McDaniel, and finally, the ball dropped to the feet of Seraina Piubel who scored. Fair dinkum McDaniel was brilliant in that exchange. She didn't have many rights to save those first two shots. She didn't have a chance with the third.
